OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1776777070
OL,3,CHigh School teacher sexually assaulted
OL,4,Cand murdered baby boy, court hears
OL,6,FITV News' Mel Barham has been at
OL,7,FPreston Crown Court as the trial
OL,8,Fbegins.
OL,10,FA former high school teacher sexually
OL,11,Fassaulted and smothered to death a
OL,12,Fbaby boy he was planning to adopt with
OL,13,Fhis partner, a court has been told.
OL,15,FPreston Davey, who was just 13-months-
OL,16,Fold, died after being ill-treated,
OL,17,Fsexually abused and physically
OL,18,Fassaulted, suffering 40 traumatic
OL,19,Finjuries, it was said.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/14
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
