FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1776777070
OL,3,CHigh School teacher sexually assaulted
OL,4,Cand murdered baby boy, court hears
OL,6,FJamie Varley is accused of killing the
OL,7,Fbaby boy, along with 25 other charges
OL,8,Fincluding sexual assault of a child
OL,9,Fand grievous bodily harm.
OL,11,FHis partner, John Mc-Gowan-
OL,12,FFazarkerley, is accused of causing or
OL,13,Fallowing the death of the child and
OL,14,Ffour other offences.
OL,16,FBoth men, who were in the process of
OL,17,Fadopting the baby boy, deny all of the
OL,18,Fcharges, as their trial at Preston
OL,19,FCrown Court began on 20 April.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/14
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1776777070
OL,3,CHigh School teacher sexually assaulted
OL,4,Cand murdered baby boy, court hears
OL,6,FDuring the prosecution's opening
OL,7,Fstatement, Peter Wright KC told the
OL,8,Fjury of six women and six men it was
OL,9,Fan "inevitably a highly emotionally
OL,10,Fcharged case".
OL,12,F"It's a terrible case because it
OL,13,Finvolves the death of a very, very
OL,14,Fyoung child," he continued.
OL,16,F"It is inevitable that it will provoke
OL,17,Fstrong feelings in anyone who hears
OL,18,Fthe details of this case."
OL,26,@xD@AOUzD@ZO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/14
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1776777070
OL,3,CHigh School teacher sexually assaulted
OL,4,Cand murdered baby boy, court hears
OL,6,FHis short life had "more than its
OL,7,Fshare of misfortune" being put in
OL,8,Femergency foster care after his birth,
OL,9,Fbut Preston had been a "perfectly
OL,10,Fhealthy boy" before the defendants
OL,11,Fbegan the process of adopting him in
OL,12,FApril of 2023.
OL,14,FBut he was admitted to hospital with
OL,15,Finjuries three times in the just under
OL,16,Ffour months after he began living with
OL,17,Fdefendants, before his death on 27
OL,18,FJuly 2023.
OL,26,@nD@TOUoD@TO]qD@XOUrD@LO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/14
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1776777070
OL,3,CHigh School teacher sexually assaulted
OL,4,Cand murdered baby boy, court hears
OL,6,FPreston had been born on 16 June 2022,
OL,7,Fand aged nine months in April 2023,
OL,8,Fplaced with the defendants for them to
OL,9,Fadopt, living at their home on
OL,10,FStaining Road, Blackpool.
OL,12,FLess than four months later, at about
OL,13,F6.30pm on 27 July 2023, he was brought
OL,14,Fto the Accident and Emergency
OL,15,FDepartment of Blackpool Victoria
OL,16,FHospital by the defendants.
OL,18,FHe was unconscious and in a state of
OL,19,Fcardiac arrest, Mr Wright told the
OL,20,Fcourt.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/14
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1776777070
OL,3,CHigh School teacher sexually assaulted
OL,4,Cand murdered baby boy, court hears
OL,6,FMedics tried to revive him but he was
OL,7,Fpronounced dead less than an hour
OL,8,Flater.
OL,10,FA post-mortem found his death to be as
OL,11,Fa result either of a smothering with a
OL,12,Fhand or soft fabric or by the
OL,13,Finsertion of an object into his mouth.
OL,15,FMr Wright continued: "As terrible as
OL,16,Fit is, this tragedy was not the result
OL,17,Fof some dreadful yet unforeseen
OL,18,Faccident, or natural phenomenon.
OL,26,@wD@VOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/14
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39707
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1776777070
OL,3,CHigh School teacher sexually assaulted
OL,4,Cand murdered baby boy, court hears
OL,6,F"The evidence gathered during the
OL,7,Finvestigation into his untimely death
OL,8,Frevealed a much more sinister
OL,9,Fpathology.
OL,11,F"We say the evidence demonstrates that
OL,12,Fhe was murdered by one of the people
OL,13,Fentrusted with his wellbeing; one of
OL,14,Fhis proposed adoptive parents.
OL,16,F"We say the person responsible for
OL,17,Fkilling Preston Davey was the
OL,18,Fdefendant, Jamie Varley."
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOUxD@AOUzD@YO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/14
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39708
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1776777070
OL,3,CHigh School teacher sexually assaulted
OL,4,Cand murdered baby boy, court hears
OL,6,F"But that was not the only tragedy to
OL,7,Fbefall him when in the care of these
OL,8,Fdefendants," the prosecutor continued.
OL,10,F"In the final months of his brief
OL,11,Flife, we say he was routinely ill-
OL,12,Ftreated, sexually abused and
OL,13,Fphysically assaulted."
OL,26,@nD@AOUpD@LO]rD@AOUuD@VO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/14
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39709
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1776777070
OL,3,CHigh School teacher sexually assaulted
OL,4,Cand murdered baby boy, court hears
OL,6,FA post-mortem showed the child had
OL,7,Fsuffered around 40 injuries over the
OL,8,Fcourse of the four months he was in
OL,9,Ftheir care, injuries including 30
OL,10,Fexternal bruises, a fracture to his
OL,11,Fupper left arm and internal bruising
OL,12,Fto his mouth, throat and other parts
OL,13,Fof his body.
OL,15,FVarley was mostly responsible, but
OL,16,Fevidence recovered by detectives
OL,17,Fimplicates both men in sexual assault
OL,18,F` and McGowan-Fazakerley, failing to
OL,19,Fprotect him, Mr Wright said.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/14
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
