OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39710
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1776777070
OL,3,CHigh School teacher sexually assaulted
OL,4,Cand murdered baby boy, court hears
OL,6,FOn the day he died at the time of or
OL,7,Fshortly before the final fatal
OL,8,Fassault, Varley had sexually assaulted
OL,9,Fthe baby causing internal injuries,
OL,10,Fwhile home alone with the child and
OL,11,Fhis co-accused out at work, it was
OL,12,Falleged.
OL,14,FAfter Varley's arrest and mobile phone
OL,15,Fwas seized, footage was found that he
OL,16,Fhad recorded earlier that day of the
OL,17,Flittle boy lying on a bed with
OL,18,Fphysical and obvious signs of
OL,19,Frespiratory arrest, but the defendant
OL,20,Fdid not attempt recovery or seek
OL,21,Fmedical help.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/14
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39711
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1776777070
OL,3,CHigh School teacher sexually assaulted
OL,4,Cand murdered baby boy, court hears
OL,6,FIt was only later that both defendants
OL,7,Ftook Preston to hospital, by which
OL,8,Ftime it was too late to save him.
OL,10,FWhile McGowan-Fazakerley was out at
OL,11,Fwork when Varley fatally assaulted
OL,12,Fhim, he had joint responsibility for
OL,13,Fcaring for the child, had daily
OL,14,Fcontact and should have been aware of
OL,15,Fwhat was going on and protected the
OL,16,Fyoungster.
OL,18,FBut not only was he aware of the
OL,19,Fabuse, he participated in it, Mr
OL,20,FWright said.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G11/14
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39712
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1776777070
OL,3,CHigh School teacher sexually assaulted
OL,4,Cand murdered baby boy, court hears
OL,6,FThe prosecutor warned jurors to "steel
OL,7,Fthemselves" as images of the child
OL,8,Fwere shown on screen, the prosecution
OL,9,Fsaid, after he had been sexually
OL,10,Fassaulted.
OL,12,FVarley had also taken a number of
OL,13,Fimages and videos of the abuse, but
OL,14,Fthese were not "happy snaps of family
OL,15,Flife" ` but indecent images, the jury
OL,16,Fwas told.
OL,18,FThe defendants appeared to be a happy,
OL,19,Fstable couple, but that was far from
OL,20,Fthe truth, Mr Wright said.
OL,26,@nD@aOUoD@KO]vD@POUwD@EO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G12/14
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39713
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1776777070
OL,3,CHigh School teacher sexually assaulted
OL,4,Cand murdered baby boy, court hears
OL,6,FVarley denies murder, manslaughter,
OL,7,Ftwo counts of assault by penetration,
OL,8,Ffive counts of cruelty to a child,
OL,9,Fgrievous bodily harm, sexual assault
OL,10,Fof a child, 13 counts of taking
OL,11,Findecent photos or videos of a child,
OL,12,Fone of distributing an indecent photo
OL,13,Fof a child, to his co-accused, and one
OL,14,Fof making an indecent photo.
OL,16,FMcGowan-Fazakerley denies allowing the
OL,17,Fdeath of a child, three counts of
OL,18,Fchild cruelty and one count of the
OL,19,Fsexual assault of a child.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G13/14
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
